fields.physical_description:
[Cart] dark breen plastic, moulded to form a retangular cart body with decorative panels on each side marked in gold
mounted on two light beige wheels with a metal axle, and one small wheel at the front which rotates
at the front is a handle bar of light beige plastic and underneath are two supports of light brown plastic
[Canopy] light brown plastic, moulded as a legged canopy with scrollwork on each end
the top is covered with a sheet of plasticized yellow and white striped cotton
top corner shaped to hold hook
[Flowerpot] moulded beige plastic

[Plant holder] beige plastic, moulded into a mushroom shape; it fits into the flowerpot
at the top is a hole to house the flower stem

[Hook] light beige plastic, moulded to represent a hook from which is hung the wrapping paper
it fits into the top left corner of the canopy
[Wrapping paper] 6 sheet of tissue paper held together at one corner by a knotted loop of white thread
[Instructions] paper printed to show diagrams of how the flower pots fit together and the canopy fits on the cart
[Box] card printed in colours to show photographs and illustrations, the maker's details, safety standards trademark and the age limits of "After 4+"
titles are in three languages
the back extends up to form a tag which has a central cut out area so that the box can be displayed
[Insert] card, white, folded and taped into shape, to hold all the various parts
